    "description": "Dumb Little Robots is a 2d puzzle game where you control robots that each have a single function. Help them work together to solve tricky levels. Meet new robots as you go and learn how they change the possibilities!<br><br>Start simply...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896720/extras/c1d08e24e15183054a059df8b7715e10.poster.avif?t=1694579822\" width=516 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896720/extras/c1d08e24e15183054a059df8b7715e10.webm?t=1694579822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896720/extras/c1d08e24e15183054a059df8b7715e10.mp4?t=1694579822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get complex!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896720/extras/0dbe422a47b50ea66fd88d85678d8c5c.poster.avif?t=1694579822\" width=340 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896720/extras/0dbe422a47b50ea66fd88d85678d8c5c.webm?t=1694579822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896720/extras/0dbe422a47b50ea66fd88d85678d8c5c.mp4?t=1694579822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Levels play out on grids, and primarily feature pushing, rotating, destroying, and copying robots to solve.<br><br>If you find yourself stuck, DON'T PANIC. This game features a hint button! And then panic anyway, as you may find the assistance sometimes less than helpful.<br><br>Includes 51 levels, divided between 6 tutorial levels and 45 main levels. Levels are clustered into groups of 9 that can be completed in any order.",
